body:
So, I&#039;m a  {{champion:163}} main and have loved playing her ever since her release. I remember when she came out she&#039;d shout things like &quot;Burst!&quot; and &quot;Erupt!&quot; when she shot that chunk upwards out of the ground (also my personal favourite: &quot;Maybe you should go over there!&quot; 

I remember these quotes are what made it feel fun playing her. However, maybe late in the summer of 2016 I noticed those quotes disappeared. I was really sad to see them go. BUT this past week I noticed they made a return with the new patch update. 

Rito... or anyone, is this intentional or have I just gone a year-ish without hearing them? I feel like they were disabled but idk. Did anyone else notice this?

replies.body:
Oh so there were Taliyah Quotes I've never seen before? Man, and to make her feel more interactive is just another part of how I love her. I approve of this.

